{"tid":2449481,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【對聯】戴罩係個人選擇，絕對尊重，但每一個散播恐懼，宣傳中武肺好易死，抗疫可以救港既，都係瘟疫政治既推手！！！","createTime":"2021-03-16T16:48:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T00:50:39.000Z","uid":88743,"like":13,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6fc6b179481c0af198194ed42ba3fb2081d49214","tid":2449481,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T16:48:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">移民係個人選擇，絕對尊重，但每一個散播恐懼，宣傳香港會變新疆，移民可以救港既，都係維穩政權既推手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n移民風＝放棄風<br />\n多一個人諗移民，就少一個人諗抗爭<br />\n<br />\n係咩人宣傳香港會變新疆，移民係抗爭手段？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"maroon\">攬炒救港</span>最後一步係<span class=\"maroon\">移民</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2445638\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2445638</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z7PQ0OW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ7PQ0OW.jpg&h=69f8a270&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n抗爭口號，有一句<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"maroon\">「不是看到了希望才去堅持，而是因為堅持了才有希望」</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/78MJ3iD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F78MJ3iD.png&h=ffba5956&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"maroon\">當時香港人再無堅持落去　寄望侵侵　已經走錯左</span></strong><br />\n到而家美國餵啲希望俾你食，香港人睇撚住緬甸，都已經唔撚信既呢啲「國際線」既同時<br />\n係咩人希望你相信外國同埋布林肯 ，仲要話唔信佢地就係五毛係鬼？<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"maroon\">all talk no action 係 PR 分化國際線既手段</span> - 個別 POST 細心分析</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2428980\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2428980</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gy08UeR.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgy08UeR.gif&h=30578714&s={SIZE}\" />​<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇返以前啲圖<br />\n<